title: [Deep Forest, Ancient Modwir]
description: A huge modwir has elbowed out all competition, and now dominates the trees around it with an air of haughty demeanor.  It stands taller than any of its neighbors, and a thick carpet of rust-colored needles obscures its foot.  Here and there, large roots protrude up out of the ground cover, gnarled and knobby, like the backs of ancient sea creatures breaking the surface of the waves before diving back into the depths.
